# Documentation Check Ignore Patterns
#
# Files matching these patterns will be excluded from the documentation
# update check when merging to main.
#
# Use glob-style patterns:
#   - * matches files in current directory
#   - ** matches across directories
#   - Lines starting with # are comments

# Exclude planning and brainstorming directories
docs/plans/**
docs/brainstorms/**

# Exclude temporary and scratch documentation
*-todo.md
*-scratch.md
*-draft.md

# Exclude internal notes
*-notes.md
NOTES.md
